Description:
STYLISH. SLEAK. AFFORDABLE
"No risk in Rix."
Located in the ever-appealing Park Central Estate, the property at Rix Road is centrally located. Walking distance to Maranatha School, Officer Train Station and moments away from the soon-to-be prominent shopping centre.
The house itself is highly functional and features"
- Three bedrooms, master with en-suite and walk-in robe;
- Open plan living/dining room;
- Modern kitchen;
- Heating and cooling;
- Double car garage with internal access;
- Your own private landscaped courtyard.
Offers before auction will be considered.
